sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard / CLI)
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Init as eval-runtime-init<br/>(Init Container)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP
    participant Adapter as Adapter Container<br/>(lm-eval-harness / etc.)
    participant Model as Model Inference<br/>Endpoint
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>Server
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Submission (Cluster Mode)
        Client->>KRBAC: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user)
        KRBAC->>EvalHub: Forward request<br/>X-Tenant + X-User headers (plaintext, pod-local)
        EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (sidecar config)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create/read Secrets (model auth, S3)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create Job (3-container pod)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        EvalHub-->>KRBAC: 201 Created (job ID, status)
        KRBAC-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Init,S3: Flow 2a: Init Container — Test Data Download
        Init->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials (Secret mount)
        S3-->>Init: Test data files
        Note over Init: Completes → Sidecar starts (KEP-753)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Sidecar,OCI: Flow 2b: Evaluation Job Execution
        Note over Sidecar: Startup probe: GET /health<br/>Sidecar ready before adapter starts

        Adapter->>Sidecar: Model inference request<br/>Auth: ref-token (synthetic)
        Sidecar->>Sidecar: Credential injection<br/>ref-token → real API key
        Sidecar->>Model: Forward request<br/>Auth: Real API key (injected)
        Model-->>Sidecar: Inference response
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response

        Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>Status update
        Sidecar->>KRBAC: Forward to eval-hub<br/>Auth: SA Token
        KRBAC->>EvalHub: Job status event<br/>X-Tenant + X-User

        Adapter->>Sidecar: MLflow tracking call<br/>POST /api/2.0/mlflow/*
        Sidecar->>MLflow: Forward<br/>Auth: SA Projected Token
        MLflow-->>Sidecar: Tracking response
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response

        Adapter->>Sidecar: OCI artifact push<br/>PUT /v2/{repo}/blobs/*
        Sidecar->>OCI: Forward<br/>Auth: Docker v2 Bearer
        OCI-->>Sidecar: Push response
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,EvalHub: Flow 3: MCP Agent Integration
        participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude / Cursor)
        participant MCPSrv as evalhub-mcp<br/>3001/TCP or stdio

        Agent->>MCPSrv: MCP JSON-RPC<br/>(submit_evaluation / get_job_status)
        MCPSrv->>EvalHub: HTTP REST call<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        EvalHub-->>MCPSrv: JSON response
        MCPSrv-->>Agent: MCP result
    end
